publisher: City of Indianapolis and Marion County - IndyGIS
keyword: [u'Election Results', u'Election Results Archive', u'Marion County Election Results', u'Indy Election Results', u'2011 Election Results', u'Political']
title: 2012 General Election Results
description:
2012 General Election Results

Contest and precinct results are presented here in an
     Excel document. Marion County reduced its number of precincts from 917
     to 590 in December 2007. Therefore, the precinct results for those
     elections occurring after December 2007 are not comparable with those
     elections?occurring before December 2007. Marion County increased the number of precincts from
     590 to 600 in December 2011. Therefore, the precinct results for those
     elections occurring after December 2011 are not comparable with those
     election occurring between December 2007 through December 2011.
